<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LABOUR ON</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Buh lakphat ahi sep ding atam hi,
 Buh a min tai, nasem mi a tawm ui;
 Lalpa'n ginuma sem di'n mi a sam,
 A hun sapna chuh ngaihsak in.

[V2]
 Sem hitiu, sem hitiu,
 Kipahman chuh en kawmin;
 Lalpa'n hatna thak ei piek ding thu A gen,
 Nisa a tum man sem hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Buh-In ah buhvui pha hun lakhawm un,
 Lunggil zangtaka kipahna la sa'n;
 Zan hungtun man theihtawp in sem hitiu,
 Thimna'n sun khawvak a suon man.

[V4]
 3. Buh atte'n kipahman tampi mun au,
 A phat chuh sawtin, nasep hak mahleh;
 A mitel te'n Lalpa kipahpih ding,
 Lungkhamna dahum nawhmang in.

[V5]
 4. En un, chung gama um van In nuom chuh,
 Theihtawp a panga, semgim te'n luoh ding;
 Lalpa hehpihna Aw chun sam intin,
 Kumsawt ni tawplo luoh tan au.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>297</hymn_number>
</song>